### QuickLendX Protocol API Playground
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_auth_token_here

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get All Invoices (Paginated)
# Returns verified invoices available for funding
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Create a New Invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "amount": 250000,
    "currency": "USDC",
    "description": "Inventory Purchase - March 2024",
    "dueDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
    "category": "GOODS"
}

### 4. Get Invoice Details
@invoiceId = some_invoice_id_from_seed
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Place a Bid
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/bids
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "bidAmount": 240000,
    "expectedReturn": 260000
}

### 6. Get Business Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Platform Analytics (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}